Srs(software requirement specification)
Introduction:
Here we are creating a website to manage library and the following are the functional and non functional requirements
Purpose:
To build a website that is able to  manage the library flawlessly 
Functional requirements:
Login:login page should be available
Books info:info about books should be available
Non function requirements:
Security: it should have a good security system
Database:it should have a large database
overview
it should have all the above features and shold not have any issues in managing th library
